| last = Isaacson | first = Walter
| authorlink = Walter Isaacson
| page = 166
| publisher = Simon & Schuster
| year = 2011
| ISBN = 1-4516-4853-7
}}</ref>

雖然乔布斯沒有太多電路板設計經驗，但是他知道他的朋友[[斯蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克|斯蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克]]有製作少量電路板的能力。乔布斯成功說服沃兹尼亚克與他合作。<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20110612071502/http://www.woz.org/letters/general/91.html ''Letters – General Questions Answered''], Woz.org</ref>為了減少電路板數量，沃兹尼亚克利用其“棘手的小設計”來設計原型。<ref name="iWoz">[[Steve_Wozniak|Wozniak, Steven]]: "[[iWoz|iWoz]]", a: pages 147–148, b: page 180. [[W._W._Norton|W. W. Norton]], 2006. ISBN 978-0-393-06143-7</ref>在開發工作接近尾聲時，沃兹尼亚克想將計分板移至螢幕的頂部，但乔布斯聲稱布什內爾想將計分板置於螢幕的底部，因此沃兹尼亚克放棄了這個想法。<ref name="UHVF">Kent, Steven: ''The Ultimate History of Video Games'', pages 71–73. Three Rivers Press, 2001. ISBN 0-7615-3643-4.</ref>二人成功在4天內完成設計，而乔布斯則獲得了5,000美金作為獎勵。可是，沃兹尼亚克並不知道5,000美金獎勵一事，因此只收了350美金作為薪酬。<ref name="DotEaters">{{Cite web |url=http://www.thedoteaters.com/p2_stage1.php |title=Player 2 Stage 1: The Coin Eaters |accessdate=2013-09-07 |archive-date=2007-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071231000817/http://www.thedoteaters.com/p2_stage1.php |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="ArcadeHistory">{{Cite web |url=http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=breakout&page=detail&id=3397 |title=Arcade History: Breakout |accessdate=2013-09-07 |archive-date=2014-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502233643/http://www.arcade-history.com/?n=breakout&page=detail&id=3397 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ClassicGaming">{{Cite web |url=http://classicgaming.gamespy.com/View.php?view=Articles.Detail&id=395 |title=Classic Gaming: A Complete History of Breakout |accessdate=2013-09-07 |archive-date=2014-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140623034804/http://classicgaming.gamespy.com/View.php?view=Articles.Detail&id=395 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

雅達利最終沒法使用沃兹尼亚克設計的原型，因為他將[[電晶體－電晶體邏輯|電晶體－電晶體邏輯]]的數量減少至42個，令到街機過於精巧和複雜，以致雅達利難以大量製造之。<ref name="iWoz"/>但是，沃兹尼亚克卻指出這是因為雅達利不能明白他的設計。<ref name="UHVF"/>最後，雅達利使用了他們自己的設計，而該設計需要高達100個電晶體－電晶體邏輯。<ref name="DotEaters"/>諷刺的是，沃兹尼亚克提出將計分板移至螢幕頂部的建議反而被接納。<ref name="ArcadeHistory"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thelogbook.com/phosphor/1970s/o.htm |title=Phosphor-Dot Fossils: Breakout<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2007-10-17 |archive-date=2007-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017131038/http://www.thelogbook.com/phosphor/1970s/o.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/1460/woz_was_here__steve_wozniak_on_.php |title=Gamasutra.com Features - Woz Was Here - Steve Wozniak On His Gaming Past<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-09-07 |archive-date=2013-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130811165959/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/1460/woz_was_here__steve_wozniak_on_.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>

